        A[Developer<br/>Commits Code]
        B[Version Control<br/>GitHub, GitLab]
        C[CI Server<br/>Jenkins, CircleCI<br/>GitHub Actions]
        D[Build<br/>Compile, Package]
        E[Test<br/>Unit, Integration, E2E]
        F[Security Scan<br/>SAST, Dependency Check]
